      "verse_key": "41:12",
      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "فَقَضَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>هُ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ سَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed>عَ سَمَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>وَا<tajweed class=ikhafa>تٍ ف</tajweed>ِى يَوْمَيْنِ وَأَوْحَىٰ فِى كُلِّ سَم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓءٍ أَمْرَهَا‌ۚ وَزَيَّ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َا <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>سَّم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓءَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>دُّنْيَا بِمَصَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>بِيحَ وَحِفْ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ظًا‌ۚ ذ</tajweed><tajweed class=madda_normal>َٲ</tajweed>لِكَ تَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>قْ</tajweed>دِيرُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعَزِيزِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعَل<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ِي</tajweed>مِ <span class=end>١٢</span>"
