      "verse_key": "41:13",
      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "فَإِنْ أَعْرَضُو<tajweed class=slnt>اْ</tajweed> فَقُلْ أَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نذ</tajweed>َرْتُكُمْ صَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>عِقَ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>ةً م</tajweed>ِّثْلَ صَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>عِقَةِ عَا<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>دٍ و</tajweed>َثَم<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>َ <span class=end>١٣</span>"
